---
title: Pulled Chilli & Lime Jackfruit Nachos with Sour Cream & Cheddar Cheese
description: Jackfruit marinated with mild chilli and lime – our new favourite (and totally irresistible) veggie alternative to pulled pork. Pair it with our tried-and-true nachos recipe that requires zero fuss assemblage and it’ll be on the plate in a flash.
